{"tid":1304213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要人啊！！！油塘要人！！！","createTime":"2019-07-10T14:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T14:35:51.000Z","uid":201683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3ebe69c51acbe82b724f4a740815e1a0ec00e8c3","tid":1304213,"uid":201683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:13:56.000Z","msg":"快<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FzX6TFU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFzX6TFU.png&h=ebea1693&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ee0b09fa58d5c53a24ac3c5c3fad47919865f45","tid":1304213,"uid":201683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:14:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"57c63ef098bf8c8ed2cb16264131e3c5adf4c7bf","tid":1304213,"uid":201683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:14:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ee0353668a1c29ec6c890f35b3ca7a9443a40f74","tid":1304213,"uid":265972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:33:04.000Z","msg":"俾廢老搞事時，如果佢地出手打人，係咪可以合力制服佢地， 一路拍片一路大聲講行使緊市民拘捕權<br />\n<br />\n《刑事訴訟程序條例》第一○一（二）條，任何人可毋須手令而逮捕任何他合理地懷疑犯了「可逮捕罪行」的人。不過，市民若要行使拘捕權，須遵守一些限制。<br />\n<br />\n        限制一：只可向觸犯了「可逮捕罪行」的人行使。按《釋義及通則條例》第三條，「可逮捕罪行」（arrestableoffence）是指法庭可判處超過十二個月監禁的罪行，例如強姦、非禮、盜竊、搶劫等。即是輕微罪行例如扔棄垃圾，便不是可逮捕罪行，大家無權拘捕垃圾蟲。<br />\n<br />\n        限制二：在行使拘捕時不可使用過份武力，在當時環境而言屬於合理的武力。<br />\n<br />\n        限制三：市民必須將被拘捕者交警員，在合理範圍內盡快將該人帶給裁判官依法處理。<br />\n<br />\n        例如，在「陳鎮坤案」（HCMA63/2012）中，超市女員工拘捕涉嫌非禮她的顧客。她當時不准被告離開，又在被告要逃走時追趕及捉住他，然後報案。法庭裁定該員工所用的武力合理，其拘捕合法。案中的小插曲是，裁判官竟然錯誤地認為「非禮」及「普通襲擊」均是可逮捕罪行。上訴庭指出，「普通襲擊」並不是可逮捕罪行，因為其最高判刑只是十二個月監禁。<br />\n<br />\n        一般人遇上罪案，可能難以分辨當時情況是否可以行使市民拘捕權。故此，大家在見義勇為拘捕了罪犯後，應該盡快交由警方處理，方為上策。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.h1.com.hk/dailynews/headline_news_detail_columnist.asp?id=309147&sect;ion_name=wtt&amp;kw=50\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.h1.com.hk%2Fdailynews%2Fheadline_news_detail_columnist.asp%3Fid%3D309147%C2%A7ion_name%3Dwtt%26kw%3D50&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3ZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=8b7f62c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.h1.com.hk/dailynews/headline_news_detail_columnist.asp?id=309147&sect;ion_name=wtt&amp;kw=50</a>"},{"pid":"cb143ef507672cfca428bb666077bd20bc67f619","tid":1304213,"uid":199108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:35:51.000Z","msg":"有鑑於無線新聞報導偏頗，誤導市民，分裂社會<br />\n現嚴正呼籲所有廣告商撤回TVB廣告，拒絕向紅媒之首提供資金，懲治其偏頗的報導手法。<br />\n<br />\n抵制TVB廣告商行動 - 第三波 <br />\n1. Hipp喜寶+美贊臣<br />\n2. Eclipse<br />\n3. 幸福傷風素<br />\n<br />\n1. Hipp喜寶+美贊臣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HiPP.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHiPP.hk&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3ZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=8e090bca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HiPP.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/meadjohnsonhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmeadjohnsonhk&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3ZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=7494a9c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/meadjohnsonhk</a><br />\n喺TVB賣廣告，成為破壞下一代成長環境的幫兇<br />\n建議替代：Nutrilon、雅培<br />\n<br />\n2. Eclipse/Extra益齒達/Airwaves (箭牌旗下)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/extrahk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fextrahk&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3ZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=b8ee471c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/extrahk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Airwaves\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAirwaves&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3ZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=79217be6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Airwaves</a><br />\n建議替代：利口樂<br />\n<br />\n3. 幸福傷風素<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Fortune.Pharmacal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFortune.Pharmacal&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3ZR